################## 
configuring each ubuntu/xenial box

Gunicorns:
vagrant up
vagrant ssh
wget --no-cache -O gunicorn.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jamangi/AppServer/master/gunicorn.sh && chmod u+x gunicorn.sh && ./gunicorn.sh

wget --no-cache -O /etc/systemd/system/myproject.service https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jamangi/AppServer/master/myproject.service
sudo systemctl start myproject
sudo systemctl enable myproject

################## 
debugging

sudo vim /var/log/syslog  (for errors)

systemctl daemon-reload   (after changing system unit file)